\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Translocations within the 
\emph on
MLL 
\emph default
gene are found in approximately 10% of all human leukaemias 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Huret2001"

\end_inset

.
 There are over 100 documented 
\emph on
MLL
\emph default
