 An internal promoter is present within the murine 
\emph on
Mll 
\emph default
breakpoint cluster region, correlating with etoposide-induced DSBs 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Scharf2007"

\end_inset

, DNase I hypersensitive sites 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Strissel1998"

\end_inset

